1213.name: E CuMnAlNi
1213.Applications:
CuMnAlNi is designed for welding and overlaying of almost all bronzes but can also be used on cast iron and most kind of steels. Due to the high tensile 
strength and the very good sliding properties it is often used for surfacing of shafts, ship propellers, bearings, dies etc…
1213.Suitable_For: joining brass, bronze, and steel, ship propellors, dies, shafts, pump parts, valves, UNS : C62300 - C63000, DIN : CuAl10Fe3Mn2 - CuAl10Ni5Fe4 - G-CuAl10Fe, Mat n° : 2.0936 - 2.0966 - 2.0940! Cunial.
